---
title: Squiggly Double Beef & Pork Hidden Veggie Pasta with Crispy Parmesan Clusters
description: It’s all hands on deck, this recipe is designed to be cooked by grown-ups and kids together! Brighten your day with another
stunning pasta sauce. There are so many combinations you can try and this tomato-based one is a standout among them.
Combine tomatoes with veggies, beef and pork to create that pasta sauce we can’t get enough of.

